data.description: Welcome to this hidden gem in this active Highland Springs 55+ Village community. This property is known to be the last undeveloped lot to be sold and built upon in the community. This gorgeous home features a modern floor plan with current touches such as bull nose drywall corners, kitchen island, recessed lighting, double pane windows, high ceilings, and so much more. Walk in and be greeted with a spacious open floor plan with a fireplace, formal dining room, indoor laundry room, primary bedroom with large walk in closet, primary bathroom featuring a jetted tub and separate walk in shower. This truly is a must see property. The seller opened up part of a wall to the 3rd bedroom to have more open living space which really makes the home feel large inside, but this can be reversed. With a 433A recorded, this property is financeable with Fha, Va, conventional etc. This home is situated on the last hole of the golf course and has views of the lake/green. You can walk to the lake and even do some fishing. Large covered parking area that is divided by a outdoor locked storage area (can be removed for more parking or for a garage) and a great outdoor private sitting area looking out on the golf course/lake. Standing at the kitchen sink you even get to enjoy golf course/lake/mountain views. Come and enjoy the community which features fishing in the lakes, a golf course, a community center with library/pool/indoor spa/tennis courts/other outdoor sports/ events hall/billiards room/golf cart parking lot/ and so much more. Added bonus, this is right by 123 farms that features events/flowers/ and lots of fun activities, walking distance from the house.
